### Technical Musings from a Design Team

Innovative design comes at the price of innovative technology. Scratch that (insert your ctrl-h's here). 

Good design needs great technology to make it work. That's basically what this space is about - getting into the greasy bits on what makes all the pieces fit and run like butter.
